channel.title: My Client Isn't Working After Compiling And Running - Please Help!
channel.description:
I updated my client.java and compiled. Then I run my server .. And after that I logged in and my old client (before updating and compiling) was still there. So I am lucky I archived my source before this happened. Now everytime I update I have to delete my source (except the updated client.java) and extract my old source back and add the updated client.java to make it work.. But now.. Not even that works! Please help I was up until 2am lastnight tryna figure out the error <.< And yes I know it's stupid but I sent my client.java to somebody and he edited it for me and sent it back so I'm guessing somehow he locked my source or something I dunno.
Thank you very much.
